	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissime vir, domine et frater colendissime, S. Rescripsi d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3988" cert="high">Ioanni Wolphio</persName>, ex quo scies, quę utriusque refert te scire, modo scribo, ut diligentissime tibi commendem filios generosi et pii viri domini <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p753">Stanislai Czikowski</persName>, de ecclesia dei optime meriti.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas alligatas his, ut d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvino</persName> reddi cures, te etiam atque etiam rogo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exemplum tuarum literarum, quibus respondes ad nescio quas literas ad te missas per d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20298" cert="high">Martinum Czechovium</persName>, ill.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">mi palatini <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l552" cert="high">Vilnensis</placeName> nuntium, ac si nomine ecclesiarum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l673" cert="high">Minoris Polonię</placeName> essent scriptę tibi mitto.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum rev [...] d. <persName type="citizen_name">Felix</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracovia</placeName> discederet, commisit mihi hanc provintiam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video tibi viro alioqui prudentissimo et d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvino</persName> fuisse impositum a nescio quo, qui titulum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviensis</placeName> ecclesię pastoris sibi usurpat, ut facilius imponat.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is persuaso quodam ministro, ambitiosi et turbulenti ingenii homine, et circumvento d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8318" cert="high">Felice Crucigero</persName> superintendente, alioqui viro integerrimo, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8480" cert="high">Martino Crovitio</persName> allecto scripsit ad te literas nomine ecclesiarum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l673" cert="high">Minoris Polonię</placeName> et inseruit quandam confessionem.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cęterum ne amplius credatis huiusmodi literis, synodus seniorum celebrata <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviae</placeName> 10. huius mensis te et d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinum</persName> per literas a superintendentibus ecclesiarum et aliquot senioribus equestris ordinis subscriptas vos facit cautos.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod in tuis ad d. <persName type="auto_name">Felicem</persName> me salvere iubes, habeo gratiam, quod vero hortaris, ut sim integer, esset, unde tecum familiariter expostulare possem, si non magis te amarem, quam tu mihi fidis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed his copiosius alias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, vir clarissime, et scias <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1936" cert="high">Lismaninum</persName> tuum errare posse, sed hereticum esse non posse nec velle.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluto per te reverenter omnes tuos et domesticos et symmistas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviae</placeName> 14. decembris 1561.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1936" cert="high">Franciscus Lismaninus</persName> ex animo tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, ec[cl]esię Tigurinę pa[sto]ri fidelissimo domino et fratri colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri alias Zurik.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
